<figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><a href="https://svanty.com/photo/22/sea-shell"><img src="https://svanty.com/files/preview/1280x853/21627760933iaan9ipqusxqusksrkdg4dt4tufck55n8iwxsuaok0flzbkedm6k8pyg7ozgzc5kq989dpvhdoteynm1viedigpkd3ia5c0ukw6r.jpg" alt=""/></a></figure>
