<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:paragraph -->
<p>Over time, the artist becomes comfortable working under certain constraints - some decisions are so obvious that he begins to perceive them as his own rule. That is why there are innumerable styles. But in all this diversity, you can see patterns that allow you to create a classification. If you''re wondering what impressionism began in what time period and in what country, we recommend you continue reading.</p>
