<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-full is-resized"><img src="https://beta.svanty.com/public/uploads/blog/2021/09/zaradka.jpg" alt="Зарядка" class="wp-image-511" width="860" height="860"/></figure></div>
