<!-- /wp:image -->

<!-- wp:paragraph -->
<p>The business has always been the most popular topic on stocks. The "running" age is considered 35-65 years old if you want to shoot "bosses", negotiations, or just a "boss-subordinate" situation. Young people are more suitable for displaying small businesses, startups. The costumes in the shot should look expensive. Stationery, papers, and accessories should be up to par. Shots in this category should exude success. <strong>Most popular stock images</strong> sell the best and make the most money.</p>
